WPKG INITR MODULE - TODO
------------------------

* Provide a base path for files. Currently /var/arxiver/deploy. Idealy it should be configurable. You should create /var/arxiver

* A way to interact with samba. Now /etc/samba should exist and wpkg configuration should be included in smb.conf with:

   include = /etc/samba/wpkg_smb.conf

